'''Paul Campion''' was the cover artist for [[The Lost Jedi Adventure Game Book|''Jedi Dawn'']] and possibly [[The Lost Jedi Adventure Game Book|''The Bounty Hunter'']], as well as ''[[The Lost Jedi Adventure Game Book]]'' that collected the two books in an omnibus edition.

Paul Campion worked as a freelance cover artist for ten years, before he completed a degree in computer animation and went on to work on feature films including ''The Lord of the Rings trilogy'', ''Constantine'' and ''Sin City''.

